cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CC, cs.IR 

This paper is about natural language processing and specifically focuses on improving text comprehension models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models and the improvement of accuracy, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new dataset, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CC (Computational Complexity). Finally, the paper mentions a human study, which could indicate that it belongs to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as well.
